name: "UNDER THE SKIN"//LOST TAPE #01//B/W SPECIAL EDITION
description:
You find an old and dusty cardboard box as you're cleaning out the attic of your new home.

The box is moldy, damp, and covered in silver spider webs.

You open the box slowly, and discover it's filled with dozens of ancient, mysterious, un-labelled video tapes.

As you reach down and pick up this particular tape, you can't be sure what drew you towards it...

And even as a cold chill runs down your spine, and your brain screams at you to put it back in the box... 

You know that you have no choice now but to watch the video.
